#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/deform/curve.rst:5
msgid "Curve Modifier"
msgstr "曲线修改器"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/deform/curve.rst:7
msgid ""
"The Curve Modifier provides a simple but efficient method of deforming a mesh along a "
"curve object."
msgstr "曲线修改器为沿着曲线物体变形提供了一种简单而高效的方法。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/deform/curve.rst:9
msgid ""
"The Curve Modifier works on a (global) dominant axis, X, Y, or Z. This means that when you "
"move your mesh in the dominant direction (by default, the X axis), the mesh will traverse "
"along the curve. Moving the mesh perpendicularly to this axis, the object will move closer "
"or further away from the curve."
msgstr ""
"曲线修改器工作在（全局）主轴，X，Y，Z上。也就是说，当你沿着主轴移动网格（默认是X轴），网格"
"会沿着曲线来回移动。沿着垂直该轴的方向移动，物体会变得更近或者远离该曲线。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/deform/curve.rst:14
msgid ""
"When you move the object beyond the curve endings the object will continue to deform based "
"on the direction vector of the curve endings."
msgstr "当你移动的幅度超过曲线的两端，物体会在曲线端点指向的向量方向上继续变形。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/deform/curve.rst:17
msgid ""
"If the curve is 3D, the *Tilt* value of its control points will be used to twist the "
"deformed object. In the :menuselection:`Curve tab --> Shape panel` under :ref:`Path/Curve-"
"Deform <curve-shape-path-curve-deform>` are options that influence the modifier."
msgstr ""

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/deform/curve.rst:25
msgid "Options"
msgstr "选项"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/deform/curve.rst:31
msgid "Curve Modifier."
msgstr "曲线修改器。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/deform/curve.rst:33
msgid "Object"
msgstr "物体"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/deform/curve.rst:34
msgid "The name of the curve object that will affect the deformed object."
msgstr "影响变形物体的曲线物体的名字。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/deform/curve.rst:35
msgid "Vertex Group"
msgstr "顶点组"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/deform/curve.rst:36
msgid ""
"A vertex group name within the deformed object. The modifier will only affect vertices "
"assigned to this group."
msgstr "形变物体的顶点数组名称。修改器只对该组的顶点生效。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/deform/curve.rst:41
msgid "Deformation Axis"
msgstr "形变轴"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/deform/curve.rst:38
msgid "This is the axis that the curve deforms along."
msgstr "*X*, *Y*, *Z*, *-X*, *-Y*, *-Z*: 曲线变形所参考的轴向。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/deform/curve.rst:40
msgid "X, Y, Z, -X, -Y, -Z"
msgstr "X, Y, Z, -X, -Y, -Z"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/deform/curve.rst:44
msgid "Example"
msgstr "示例"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/deform/curve.rst:46
msgid "Let us make a simple example:"
msgstr "来一个简单的例子："

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/deform/curve.rst:48
msgid ""
"Remove the default cube object from the scene and add a Monkey with :menuselection:`Add --"
"> Mesh --> Monkey`."
msgstr "移除场景中默认的立方体，添加猴头（:menuselection:`Add --> Mesh --> Monkey`）"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/deform/curve.rst:50
msgid "Now add a curve with :menuselection:`Add --> Curve --> Bézier Curve`."
msgstr "添加一条曲线（:menuselection:`Add --> Curve --> Bezier Curve`）"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/deform/curve.rst:51
msgid ""
"While in Edit Mode, move the control points of the curve as shown in Fig. :ref:`fig-"
"modifier-curve-edit`, then exit Edit Mode :kbd:`Tab`."
msgstr ""
"在编辑模式下移动曲线的控制点，如图 :ref:`fig-modifier-curve-edit` 所示，然后退出编辑模式（:"
"kbd:`Tab`）。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/deform/curve.rst:53
msgid "Select the Monkey :kbd:`RMB` in *Object Mode* and add the Curve Modifier."
msgstr "在 *物体模式* 下选择猴头（:kbd:`RMB`）。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/deform/curve.rst:54
msgid ""
"Assign the Bézier curve to the modifier, as shown in Fig. :ref:`fig-modifier-curve-panel`. "
"The Monkey should be positioned on the curve."
msgstr "如图 :ref:`fig-modifier-curve-panel` 所示，将曲线指定为修改器。猴头放在曲线上。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/deform/curve.rst:64
msgid "Edit curve."
msgstr "编辑曲线。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/deform/curve.rst:69
msgid "Monkey on a curve."
msgstr "曲线上的猴头。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/deform/curve.rst:74
msgid "Monkey deformations."
msgstr "猴头变形。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/deform/curve.rst:76
msgid ""
"Now if you select the Monkey, and move it in the Y direction :kbd:`G Y`, the monkey will "
"deform nicely along the curve."
msgstr "现在如果你选择猴头，并沿着Y方向移动（:kbd:`G, Y`），猴头会很好地沿着曲线变形。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/deform/curve.rst:81
msgid ""
"If you press :kbd:`MMB` (or one of :kbd:`X`, :kbd:`Y`, :kbd:`Z`) while moving the Monkey "
"you will constrain the movement to one axis only."
msgstr "如果在移动猴头的时候按下了鼠标中键 :kbd:`MMB`，你会限制在一个轴上移动。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/deform/curve.rst:84
msgid ""
"In the image above you can see the Monkey at different positions along the curve. To get a "
"cleaner view over the deformation, a :doc:`Subdivision Surface </modeling/modifiers/"
"generate/subsurf>` Modifier with two subdivision levels was applied, and :ref:`smooth "
"<modeling-meshes-editing-normals-shading>` shading was used."
msgstr ""
"在上面的图中，你可以看到沿着曲线不同位置的猴头。为了得到变形过程中更清楚的视图，上图使用"
"了 :doc:`细分 </modeling/modifiers/generate/subsurf>` 修改器并用了两个细分级别，同时也用"
"了 :ref:`平滑 <modeling-meshes-editing-normals-shading>` 着色。"

